events.name: ファストトラベル移動場所
ファストトラベル移動場所

parameters:
Captain Agwa: There were twists and turns, but thanks to
everyone, it seems we can safely resume our work.

Captain Agwa: From now on, we will continue to rely on the
Adventurer's Guild. In addition to the promised rewards, we
also want you to accept our feelings.

Captain Agwa: I'll hand the pirates over to the guards. If
anything happens, let me know and I'll send the ship
anywhere.

Local Girl: If you're expecting to meet someone, this town
is the place! Even Mama found Papa at the beach!

Man who came on vacation: Coming here to refresh was the
right decision! I even had a wonderful encounter at the
sea...

Seductive Woman: I met him at the sea... I just love men who
have girlfriends.

Man who came on vacation: Coming here to refresh was the
right decision! I even had a wonderful encounter at the
sea...

Seductive Woman: I met him at the sea... I just love men who
have girlfriends.

Wandering Traveler: Have you heard the story of the pirates?
Even after the war with Tarasa ended, the sea remains in a
state of turmoil.

Wandering Traveler: Have you heard the story of the pirates?
Even after the war with Tarasa ended, the sea remains in a
state of turmoil.

Woman seeking encounters: You... have a handsome face...!
But don't worry... I'm in a swimsuit, so I'll take the lead.

Woman seeking encounters: Y-You look amazing in that
swimsuit...! Stop it, I won't stand a chance against you!

Woman seeking encounters: You... have a handsome face...!
But don't worry... I'm in a swimsuit, so I'll take the lead.

Restaurant Miro's Waitress: How about the best meal for your
travel memories? We have prepared the finest dishes and
wines for today as well.

Fisherman: We've caught the best fish! You should definitely
go to Restaurant MiRo!
Clea: Is it possible to obtain seashells?

Fisherman Man: I can give them to you, but there are
conditions! Would you be willing to help with fishing as a
rule of the sea?

Fisherman Man: If you have a swimsuit near the beach where
the desired seashells are, it would be better to change into
it before.
Clea: Understood, I will help you.
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置

Fisherman Man: The clams are hiding in unexpected places, so
do your best.
Fisherman: Oh, is this enough? Are this many sufficient?
Thief Nora: Um, if possible, I would like a little more...
Fisherman: Hey, hey, who are you guys?

Fisherman Companion: I heard that the beauties are gathering
shells.

Fisherman Companion: Haha, looks like reinforcements have
arrived!

Fisherman Companion: Alright, let me show you the skills of
a fisherman!
Clea: Thank you so much for this many!

Fisherman Companion: I want to thank you guys so much for
this!

Fisherman Companion: The contrast between your youthful face
and body is amazing!

Fisherman Companion: A body full of wildness! Yet, the timid
atmosphere tickles a man's heart!

Fisherman Companion: Sigh... Your overwhelming sexiness is
making me dizzy. But it's probably best to refrain from
walking by the sea while drinking alcohol.
Fisherman Companion: You... have a cute swimsuit!

Mage Relm: I knew it! Honestly, we're not just for show, you
know!

Fisherman Companion: All we need are shells, right? I'll
apologize to my companions with the best shell dish.
Mage Relm: Hmph, please satisfy my tongue!

Priestess Sophia: Nora-chan, are you okay? Not being happy
about the feast, I wonder if you're feeling unwell.
Mage Relm: I think that's quite a rude remark...

Thief Nora: I-I'm fine, you know! Let's hurry up and go eat
the feast!
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置

Fisherman: Come and visit even in your private time! This
place has the most beautiful sea in the empire, you know.
Male Merchant: Now, the specialty salted fish is on sale!
Receptionist Piste: Long time no see.

Merchant Man: Isn't that Piste-san!? What brings you here
today? And where are the Agonia-san?
Receptionist Piste: They are the escorts for today!

Merchant Man: The Adventurer's Guild has not only beautiful
receptionists, but also beautiful members!

Receptionist Piste: Hehe, you're quite skilled. Since you're
good at business, how about giving me a little extra?

Merchant Man: Haha, I can't compete with that. Just wait a
moment, I'll prepare that thing we talked about.

Priestess Sophia: There was talk about reproducing a dish,
but this is also one of the necessary ingredients, isn't it?

Receptionist Piste: That's right! I've been experimenting
and trying different things all this time.

Receptionist Piste: Finally, I found the recipe written by
the person themselves!
Merchant Man: Hey, here's the salted fish.
Receptionist Piste: Thank you very much!

Merchant Man: It's really nostalgic. She was such a small
child, but she grew up to be beautiful.

Merchant Man: I really wanted to show her my impressive
figure... to that person, truly.

Merchant Man: I'm sorry, but as you get older, things just
don't work the same way...

Receptionist Piste: It's fine! Please continue working here
so that I can come back again, okay?

Merchant Man: Of course! Please give my regards to Agonia-
san and the others!

Receptionist Piste: Alright, let's go to the next location!
Um... the next important ingredient can be found at--
Priestess Sophia: Clea-chan, is there something you need...?

Clea: It might just be my imagination, but I felt someone's
gaze. The Adventurer's Guild is an organization with many
enemies.
Clea: It might be better not to let your guard down.
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置

Male Merchant: Please give my regards to Agonia-san and the
others!
Thief Nora: ...I snuck out of the inn on my own.
Thief Nora: ...The food was delicious too.
Thief Nora: Even though I should be satisfied...
Do you want to skip the adult scene?
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置
EV：ソフィア以外+水着着用外のソフィアで話しかけると発生

Priestess Sophia: Such interesting outfits for a beach,
don't you think?

Hurried Young Man: I have a reason and it seems like I'll be
arriving late. Do you happen to know the building on this
map?

Priestess Sophia: Yes, of course. It's a bit far, so please
let me guide you.

Priestess Sophia: I was just about to separate from my
friends.
It would be helpful, I'm called Metoki.
Clea: Let's meet up later then.
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置

Hurried Young Man: I apologize, but I have a promise to meet
with my friends!

Hurried Young Man: I apologize, but I have a promise to meet
with my friends!
Cleric Sophia: I'm truly sorry for what happened.

Ojousama Metoki: It's fine... I'm quite late, but she should
forgive me.
Ojousama Metoki: Oh, right! May I ask for your name?

Cleric Sophia: Hehe, it would be lovely to keep it a secret,
wouldn't it? Meeting an unknown woman by the sea.

Ojousama Metoki: She was a wonderful woman... I hope we can
meet again somewhere someday.

Ojousama Metoki: Hey, hey! Roan! Why are you a guard? What
happened!?

Ojousama Metoki: Guard-san, there must be some mistake!
There's no way my friend would do something that would get
them arrested!

Criminal Roan: Shut up! Playing friends was just a way to
use you!

Criminal Roan: I tried to make you transport drugs using
you!

Ojousama Metoki: T-That's... that can't be true, please tell
me it's a lie!

Ojousama Metoki: Hey, Roan... You were my first friend, and
yet...

Friend Roan: Spending the night drinking with you... was
fun.
Thief Nora: It's so sad... Ugh, I feel like crying.

Clea: I think our friendship was already falling apart,
unrelated to this request.

Priestess Sophia: I believe that Metoki-san will be able to
recover. In a long life like his, there will surely be happy
encounters.

Mage Relm: Um... Are we going to be okay? I somehow feel
like Metoki-san and I are similar...

Priestess Sophia: Hehe, don't worry, everything will be
fine.
Mage Relm: Why are you so sure?

Priestess Sophia: I believe that as long as I'm with these
children, everything will be fine.
Mage Relm: It doesn't make sense as a reason.

Priestess Sophia: I believe that our friendship is based on
a connection where we don't need reasons or evidence.
Mage Relm: It's not at all logical, but... I support it.

Priestess Sophia: Hehe, let's receive our reward from the
butler and return to our journey.
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置
